Why do I feel less productive working from home?
Why do I feel like I'm going crazy?
What is cabin fever? 
It's been almost 2 weeks since the CB started. Some of us might feel lethargic, unproductive, and even more depressed while working from home. We speak to an expert to find out why we feel this way, and what you can do to make WFH better.
Wfh....longer hours, more things to be done! More house chores to do too...😜
Wow i know this Doctor.....so proud
I like this dr, learn abt the paradox thingy. He made me feel okay not to feel productive. Tbh, this wfh feels like free AL woooohoooo!

@chewthesky @cniowhhhh @kiahiann 
omg its our ethics prof!!! omg
I feel absolutely fine working from home. I’m not complaining!
Life is like a game of chess. One wrong move will have disastrous consequences! 🇸🇬
I love this guy. There's so much wisdom in his words. Ambitious as we are, as Singaporeans, we can all learn to be kinder to ourselves and each other as we deal with these difficult times 🙏
I am completely unproductive. I don’t care
Hello, to Earn from Home, I’m the Best Agent you need to contact 💰💰💰📈➡️
@mrshin10 Pls take the time to make some tiktok videos
The BGM is so distracting from the speaker's VO.
Then why I feel so happy.
Knn stop trying to take work from home away leh
